---
title: "invalidateOrders (GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_role_check: caller has ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE
    q_role_check --> q_err_role: caller lacks role
    q_err_role --> [*]: revert AccessControlUnauthorizedAccount
    q_role_check --> q_iter: i = 0
    q_iter --> q_invalidate: i < orderUids.length
    q_invalidate --> q_next: i_gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUids[i])
    q_next --> q_iter: i = i + 1
    q_iter --> [*]: i >= orderUids.length

    note right of q_iter
        INV-001: Only ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE can invalidate orders
        INV-002: All provided order UIDs are forwarded to GPv2Settlement for invalidation
        INV-003: Loop processes all order UIDs without early exit
    end note
